description: Luna Guru can give you the date and time for full or new moon. You can ask for either the next upcoming full or new moon or for one in a future month.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask Luna Guru when is Full moon in feburary
Ask Luna Guru when is next New moon
Ask Luna Guru when is Full moon in March
name: Lunar Phase Information
shortDescription: Luna Guru provides full and new moon information
